snippet.title: PlayStation - Simple Character 2000 Series Vol 03 - Kamen Rider - The Bike Race (2001)
snippet.description:
DESCRIPTION
The Bike Race: Kamen Rider is a Racing game, developed by Highwaystar and published by Bandai, which was released in Japan in 2001.
